# Playwright Automation Framework

This project demonstrates a scalable test automation framework built using Playwright.

## Key Highlights:

✔ Page Object Model (POM) implemented
✔ Reusable and maintainable test structure
✔ Automated UI test scenarios
✔ Easy test execution and reporting

## What I Offer:

* End-to-end automation using Playwright
* Framework setup from scratch
* Bug identification and reporting

## Run Tests:

npm install
npx playwright test



